&gt; To avoid this issue, you can add a timezone parameter to <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/hubl/filters#datetimeformat|the datetimeformat filter> within each hubdb module. For example, adding the ‘GMT’ as the timezone, so that dates on the page are converted in UTC 0 time, and now reflect the dates in the HubDB interface:
&gt; {{ date|datetimeformat(‘%b %d, %Y’, ‘GMT’) }}
